{"type": "article", "id": 18731, "title": "婴儿食品包装", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-09T07:10:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702125501uQUNbozFGPZqa0RA.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是专为婴儿提供的食物，材料源于小批量种植的水果蔬菜，并保证无糖以及不添加任何防腐剂。包装的设计者使用了纯白色的背景，上面将对应的蔬果排列成特殊的几何图案，有些是单个的水果，有些是混合搭配，很有童趣。此外，每一个盒子里都带有可给婴儿使用的蓝色小勺，很方便。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125457eypfQGiU7BxvlNRK.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"540\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125459Ck1aiBzmgqxtDMJ8.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"540\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125459jJOmKTe2rUwZXqya.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"540\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125500DZMPq2rQjnxUVBCO.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"708\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.65555556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021255002qVhoXHOS5Qy4fAF.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"540\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n"}